\c 5
\nb
\v 1 Nekuti mupristi mukuru mumwe nomumwe wakatorwa pakati pevanhu, unogadzirwa vanhu pazvinhu zvaMwari, kuti abayire zvose zvipo nezvibayiro nekuda kwezvivi;
\v 2 iye une moyo munyoro pane vasingazivi naivo vakatsauka, naizvozvo naiyewo amene wakakomberedzwa neutera.
\v 3 Uye nekuda kwaizvozvi iye unofanira kuzvibayira pamusoro pezvivi \add zvake\add*, sezvaanobayira zvavanhu.
\v 4 Hakuna munhu ungazvitorera rukudzo urwu, asi uyo wakadamwa naMwari saAroni.
\v 5 Saizvozvowo Kristu haana kuzvikudza iye kuva mupristi mukuru, asi uyo wakati kwaari: Ndiwe Mwanakomana wangu, Nhasi ndakubereka;
\v 6 Sezvaanorevawo pane imwe \add nzvimbo, achiti\add*: Ndiwe Mupristi nokusingaperi wenhevedzo \add yeimba\add* yaMerikizedheki.
\v 7 Iye pamazuva enyama yake, apa minyengetero nemikumbiro nekuchema kukuru nemisodzi kuna iye waigona kumuponesa parufu, uye akanzwikwa pakuti wakatya Mwari;
\v 8 kunyange aiva Mwanakomana, zvakadaro wakadzidza kuteerera nekuda kwezvinhu zvaakatambudzika;
\v 9 akati aitwa wakaperera, akazova muvambi wekuponeswa kusingaperi kuna vose avo vanomuteerera;
\v 10 akaidzwa naMwari Mupristi mukuru wenhevedzo yeimba yaMerikizedheki.
\s Vatendi vanofanira kupfuvurira mberi parutendo
\p
\v 11 Watine zvinhu zvizhinji zvatingataura pamusoro pake, zvinorema kududzira, zvamakagomara pakunzwa.
\v 12 Nekuti apo pamaifanira kuva vadzidzisi, nekuda kwenguva makashaiwa kuti kuve neunokudzidzisai kuti zviga zvekutanga zvezvimiso zvaMwari zvinyi, uye mava savanoda mukaka, kwete chikafu chikukutu.
\v 13 Nekuti ani nani unodya mukaka haana unyanzvi mushoko rekururama, nekuti mucheche.
\v 14 Asi chikafu chikukutu ndechevakura zvakazara, vanokuziva kwakadzidziswa nenzira yekurovedzwa, kuzivisisa zvose zvakanaka nezvakaipa.
